        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for gift of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p>  
<p>GB sent copies of his <hi rend="italic">Fisica del globo</hi> [1868] to Lyell and the presidents of British scientific societies but has received no acknowledgment; asks CD to check that they received the work. Could CD arrange for a notice of the book to appear in England?</p> 
